messages.message: Hi all, at 9am PT today the flow team will have a team meeting that we chat about a new product - the flow review dashboard that is designed to help operators quickly find jobs that required review and understand review progress. It’s shipped to NatWest with the December release and will be used by all customers using Instabase to do human review going forward. If you’re interested, here’s the zoom link (https://instabase.zoom.us/j/92606055130?pwd=VGtjM3BMZjNKbnRQeEsrTGdMUitoUT09) and you’re welcome to join :slightly_smiling_face:

Here’s the meeting recording for people who are interested :slightly_smiling_face:
